{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_13_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 2話 結婚記念ウエディングセール",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてみんなが私が結婚するだなんて\n誤解しているのか、理由が分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I finally figured out why everyone\nis misunderstanding that I'm getting married.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの同級生が、私がこれから結婚式をするんだと\n勘違いして、友達に連絡したそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That classmate from earlier thought I was having a wedding‚\nso she contacted all her friends.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.4202500025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "しかも私と{user}さんが\n一緒に写った写真を送信したらしくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And apparently‚ she sent out\na photo of me and {user} together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.1154167174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ということは……\n俺が怜の結婚相手だと思われているのか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Which means…\nI'm being seen as your groom-to-be!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "そうみたいです……すみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems so… I'm sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.3370944339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.7428454081
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、友達には勘違いだと伝えて\nみんなに訂正するように言っておきましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I told my friends it was a mistake\nand told them to correct everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4747609138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.3298663138
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、良かった……\n誤解は解けたんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ thank goodness…\nThe misunderstanding is cleared up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4830.9505621,
          "startTime": 42.4642838954
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8964.283895400002,
          "startTime": 46.5976172287
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.659639422
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.7976172287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "これで騒ぎも収まると思うので安心して……\nあら？　またメッセが来てますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fuss should die down now‚ so don't worry…\nOh? I got another message.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.9642838954,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7433.338165199999,
          "startTime": 51.3976220606
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16766.671498499996,
          "startTime": 60.7309553939
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.1513118424
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "高校の先生から……？　「ご両親も同意の上だとは思う\nが結婚の話を詳しく聞きたいから明日職員室に……」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From my high school teacher…? \"I assume your parents agreed‚\nbut come to the staff room tomorrow to discuss your marriage…\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6630.9553939000025,
          "startTime": 62.0309553939
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.869936307
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、昔お世話になったダンススクールの先生からも\nメッセが来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ my old dance school teacher\nsent a message too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4642887273,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8866.659545800005,
          "startTime": 74.3309482731
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9899.9964395,
          "startTime": 75.3642851668
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.1068738299
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "「結婚おめでとう、スクールのみんなも祝福してるよ\nまさか怜ちゃんに先を越されるなんて……」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Congrats on your wedding! Everyone at the school is cheering.\nI can't believe Rei beat us to it…\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0309497991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.0955823259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！　今度はスーパータケミヤの店長から！？\n一体どうなってるのよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What! This time from the manager of Super Takemiya!?\nWhat on earth is happening!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.5976185002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.7483768143
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "「結婚おめでとう、従業員一同、喜んでいるよ\n結婚祝いにブリの安売りセールをするから……」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Congratulations on the marriage! All the employees are happy.\nWe're having a yellowtail sale to celebrate your wedding…\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.7309574284,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6535.714070099999,
          "startTime": 93.2666714985
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10268.549855499998,
          "startTime": 96.9995072839
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんだって！？　早く噂を止めないと大変なことに……\nおや？　今度は俺に電話だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? If we don't stop the rumors fast‚ it'll be a disaster…\nOh? Now I'm getting a call.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5333422342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.3600611049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし……えっ！？　はい、ご無沙汰しております\nいえ、それは……はい……分かりました、すぐに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello… WHAT!? Yes‚ it's been a long time.\nNo‚ that's… yes… I understand‚ immediately…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6666755675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.2484056154
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\n顔色が真っ青ですよ。誰から電話だったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}…\nYou've gone pale. Who was on the phone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3742685156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "怜、どうやら遅かったみたいだ……怜のお父さんから\n大事な話があるから、今すぐ家に来いって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei‚ it looks like we're too late… Your father called.\nHe has something important to say and wants me at your house now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.4666755675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― One hour later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.0430963833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.1764185269
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.1764185269
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "もう、お父さんまで勘違いするなんて！\n私が結婚するなんてありえないわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ even Dad misunderstood!\nThere's no way I'm getting married!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3573558964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.3574400584
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "でも誤解が解けて良かったよ。お父さんの俺を見る目が\n怖くて、いつ殴られるかとヒヤヒヤしたからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I'm glad the misunderstanding is cleared. Your dad's glare\nwas so scary‚ I was terrified he might punch me any second.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.2000124613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ichinoseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ichinoseliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.3531050682
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "撮影スタッフの到着が遅れているおかげで\nお父さんに会う時間が出来て良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since the filming staff was running late‚\nI'm glad we had time to see Dad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.6261030671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_02-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "もし撮影が始まっていたら、お父さんに説明出来なくて\n誤解がさらに広まっていたかもしれません",
      "translations": {
